{"name": "pydev-toy", "metadata": {"name": "pydev-toy", "version": "0.0.1", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["build", "click", "tomli", "twine"], "summary": null, "upload_time": 1733094207}, "documentation": ["# Command line utils to manage simple python projects \n\nSet of command line utils to manage `pyproject.toml` based projects.\nThe tool `pydev` is built with `click` and can run multiple project\nrelated tasks in sequence from the command line.\n\n```console\npydev clean build dump\n```\n\nThis project is exploratory and may be found usefull as basis for custom workflows.\nThe project uses standard python packaging tools like `build` and `twine`\nindependently from any build backend like `setuptools`, `hatch`, `pdm`, etc ...\n\n\n## Usage\n\n```console\nUsage: pydev [OPTIONS] COMMAND1 [ARGS]... [COMMAND2 [ARGS]...]...\n\nOptions:\n  --help  Show this message and exit.\n\nCommands:\n  build    Build project wheel\n  clean    Delete build and dist folders\n  dump     Dump wheel and dist contents\n  info     Project information\n  prune    Delete all runtime folders\n  publish  Publish project with twine\n  pwd      Project root path\n  which    Locate python by version and target\n```\n\n\n## Installation\n\nThe `pydev` tool is best installed as a script in a separate ennvironment using `pipx` or `uv tool`.\n\n```console\npipx install git+https://github.com/furechan/pydev-tool.git\n```\n\n## Related Projects & Resources\n- [Packaging tools](https://sinoroc.gitlab.io/kb/python/packaging_tools_comparisons.html) Comparison of different packaging tools\n- [setuptools](https://setuptools.pypa.io/en/latest/) Setuptools is a fully-featured, actively-maintained, and stable library designed to facilitate packaging Python projects.\n- [hatch](https://hatch.pypa.io/latest/) Hatch is a modern, extensible Python project manager.\n- [pdm](https://pdm-project.org/en/latest/) Modern Python package and dependency manager supporting the latest PEP standards \n- [click](https://click.palletsprojects.com/) Python composable command line interface toolkit\n- [build](https://github.com/pypa/build) A simple, correct Python build frontend\n- [twine](https://github.com/pypa/twine/) Utilities for interacting with PyPI\n"], "modules": [{"name": "pydev.program", "documentation": ["pydev program"], "functions": [{"name": "pydev.program.main", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pydev.program.pwd", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Run pwd"]}, {"name": "pydev.program.info", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Project information"]}, {"name": "pydev.program.clean", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Delete build and dist folders"]}, {"name": "pydev.program.prune", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "yes", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Delete all runtime folders"]}, {"name": "pydev.program.build", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Build project wheel"]}, {"name": "pydev.program.dump", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Dump wheel and dist contents"]}, {"name": "pydev.program.publish", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "test_pypi", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Publish project with twine"]}, {"name": "pydev.program.which", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "version", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "target", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Locate python by version and target"]}], "variables": [{"name": "pydev.program.logger", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "pydev.utils", "documentation": ["pydev utils"], "functions": [{"name": "pydev.utils.get_python", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Python executable path for sub commands\n\nReturn:\n    Python executable where the package is installed.\n    This could be changed to use the python from\n    the system path or a virtual env."]}, {"name": "pydev.utils.get_project_root", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "strict", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Walk up to find pyproject.toml"]}, {"name": "pydev.utils.run_command", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "command", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "echo", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "strict", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "chgdir", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Run shell command"]}, {"name": "pydev.utils.load_config", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Load pyproject.toml file"]}, {"name": "pydev.utils.get_config", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "item", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "default", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Query pyproject.toml file"]}, {"name": "pydev.utils.search_path", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "pattern", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "path", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Search items in path"]}, {"name": "pydev.utils.system_python", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "version", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Python in the system path"]}, {"name": "pydev.utils.pyenv_versions", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["pyenv versions"]}, {"name": "pydev.utils.pyenv_python", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "version", "type